Class Namespace

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.sonar.Namespace
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClientNamespace, ServerNamespace
public abstract class Namespace extends Object
A namespace is a mapping of names to objects.
Author:
Douglas Lau
